1. Purpose

Grey M1 solver a la Radice et al. 2022 [arXiv:2111.14858].

This code needs 2 ghost cells on unigrid and 4 ghost cells with AMR.

A. Acknowledgements

This code is ported from THC_M1 (https://bitbucket.org/FreeTHC/thccore/src/master/) of Radice et al. 
